\cf4 # When did you start doing web stuff?\
\
Probably in \'a01995 or 1996. I was about 10 years old and my Dad installed a new app on our home computer called Internet Explorer. From that moment on I've always been fascinated by the internet. I'm fascinated by the endless possibilities the web affords, and the fact that anyone with a text editor can make an impact upon it.\
